%N A189568 Number of permutations p of 1,2,...,n satisfying |p(i+3)-p(i)|<>4 and |p(j+4)-p(j)|<>3 for all i=1..n-3, j=1..n-4.
%C A189568 a(n) is also the number of ways to place n nonattacking pieces rook + leaper[3,4] on an n X n chessboard.
%H A189568 Vaclav Kotesovec, <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/User:Vaclav_Kotesovec">Number of ways of placing non-attacking queens, kings, bishops and knights</a> (in English and Czech)
%F A189568 Asymptotic: a(n)/n! ~ 1/e^4.
